#10041
withered dryad~
a withered dryad~
A withered dryad stands here, her form ancient and desiccated and radiating a cold hostility that is not the hostility of the newly corrupted but of something that has had centuries to refine its grievances.

~
She was old when the corruption found her, and the corruption found in her a consciousness experienced enough to be genuinely dangerous; she has had time to understand exactly what she lost and to develop sophisticated opinions about those responsible.

~
