mosswort queen~
a mosswort queen~
A mosswort queen moves through the undergrowth, substantially larger than the standard mosswort beetles and carrying the additional weight of a reproductive apparatus that takes up most of her posterior section.

~
The mosswort queen does not need to fight well because everything in her immediate vicinity does the fighting for her; she is never encountered entirely alone, and the drones that accompany her are considerably less concerned with their own safety than with hers.

~
