#10043
verdant hulk~
a verdant hulk~
A verdant hulk moves through the forest, its bulk so substantial that it does not navigate the undergrowth so much as relocate it, pushing through obstacles that would stop a smaller creature without registering the resistance.

~
The verdant hulk is a plant-beast amalgamation that the Verdant Depths has been building for centuries, each generation larger and denser than the last; it is the forest's answer to the question of what happens when you give something the structural integrity of old-growth timber and the aggression of everything the forest has learned to be.

~
