bog troll~
a bog troll~
A bog troll stands here, its body covered in a thick layer of living moss and algae that makes it appear to be a mobile section of the forest floor that has acquired an opinion about intruders.

~
The bog troll's relationship with the forest is reciprocal; the moss that covers it provides camouflage and the troll provides the moss with a mobile delivery system for its spores, an arrangement that neither party negotiated consciously but both benefit from.

~
