fungal broodmother~
a fungal broodmother~
A fungal broodmother occupies a substantial section of the blightwood's interior, her body the largest single fungal organism in this zone and her presence the source of most of the spore-density in the immediate vicinity.

~
The fungal broodmother is the Blightwood Ancient's primary reproductive instrument in this zone; she produces and places the spores that become the other fungal organisms, which means killing her reduces the blightwood's capacity to replenish its forces in ways that matter to those planning extended operations here.

~
