an ancient moss elemental~
An ancient moss elemental occupies the space before you, its form composed of living moss compressed and animated into something between a creature and a force of nature.

~
The ancient moss elemental is an elemental not in the sense of having been summoned from another plane but in the sense of having condensed from the forest itself; it is a concentration of the forest's living essence given enough density and direction to qualify as an individual, though that individuality is provisional.

~
