#10051
twisted ent~
a twisted ent~
A twisted ent moves through the forest, its form the corrupted version of the treant species -- the same fundamental architecture but distorted by a process that has replaced deliberate growth with something more urgent and less stable.

~
The twisted ent has been corrupted not by external agency but by an internal process -- the forest's will turning inward and accelerating the ent's growth beyond what the original form was designed to sustain; the result is a creature that is both more powerful and less coherent than an uncorrupted treant.

~
