thornveil assassin~
a thornveil assassin~
A thornveil assassin moves through the deep forest in a pattern that makes it genuinely difficult to determine its position even when it is visible, the movement itself serving as a form of concealment.

~
The thornveil assassin is the forest's most evolved predatory plant-form -- mobile, patient, and capable of a degree of tactical reasoning that conventional plant biology cannot produce; it selects targets based on criteria that no other plant-form applies, which suggests a level of assessment that the forest has been working toward for a very long time.

~
