sap ooze~
a sap ooze~
A sap ooze moves across the forest floor as a slow-spreading mass of semi-solid amber tree sap, its surface dimly luminescent and its motion the patient spread of something that is in no hurry.

~
The sap ooze is the forest's most basic animated construct -- tree sap given the minimum necessary coherence to pursue nutrition -- and it has been doing exactly this, in this exact manner, for longer than most of the other organisms in this forest have existed.

~
