feral grove keeper~
a feral grove keeper~
A feral grove keeper stands here, its form retaining the outline of the nature guardian it once was while every detail of that form has been taken over by something with different priorities.

~
The grove keeper was created to protect a specific grove and given the intelligence to do so effectively; the corruption that took it has retained the intelligence and redirected it entirely, which means a corrupted grove keeper is not less capable than its uncorrupted equivalent -- it is equally capable in pursuit of opposite goals.

~
