thornroot drake~
a thornroot drake~
A thornroot drake occupies a clearing, its body the rough outline of a large reptile assembled from compressed root-and-thorn material over a framework of living wood, its eyes amber sap in sealed amber casings.

~
The thornroot drake is the forest's response to the question of what form the apex of plant-based predation would take; the answer is something with the mass and aggression of a large reptile combined with the structural properties of the Verdant Depths' densest root-material, and the answer is also capable of moving considerably faster than it appears able to.

~
