#10061
Rootmother~
the Rootmother~
The Rootmother is here, her form filling the sanctum -- root and branch and heartwood and flowering tendril, all of it alive, all of it her, all of it watching you with an attention that predates everything else in this forest.

~
She is not a creature that grew into this form and not a goddess that assumed it; she is the forest's own will concentrated into something dense enough to respond to what stands in front of her, and what stands in front of her has been considered and found insufficient -- not threatening, not worthy of fear, simply a problem that her domain will correct, as it has corrected everything that has entered the sanctum before you and will correct everything that comes after.

Her roots extend in every direction into the living rock, drawing nourishment from depths that daylight has never reached, and the flowers that bloom from her uppermost branches produce a bioluminescence that fills the sanctum with warm, deceptive light -- the most beautiful thing in the Verdant Depths and the last thing many have seen.

~
