#10063
Thornfang Alpha~
Thornfang Alpha~
Thornfang Alpha is here, occupying the center of its lair with the absolute stillness of something that has no need to signal dominance because the lair itself does that already.

~
The Alpha is the apex of the Verdant Depths' predation hierarchy -- the thing that every other predator in this forest has learned to avoid, the creature at the top of a system it did not build but has perfected over decades of competition with everything the forest produces.

It is larger than the packmates, faster than the stalkers, and more patient than either; it has survived long enough in this environment to have fought and killed every category of threat this forest generates, which means it has seen something like you before, has identified the category you belong to, and has already formulated its response before you are aware that you are being assessed.

~
